long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Mr.Pong is a fun skill game where we try to earn points by jumping and paying attention to the obstacles with the cube.

In this area, encryption is blocking on the right and left. We bounce and score points by paying attention to this obstacle. We continue to play by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Mr.Pong has come out to see it as a game of skill. That has prepared without children's play in mind and is challenging for us.
